    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mas, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You spit out a large quantity of sticky liquid that covers the area. Creatures within the area cannot run or charge, and move at half their speed during their turn. They also suffer a -2 penalty to Defense and Reflex saves. Characters that use the Tadayou technique before moving through the area remain unaffected</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to increase the Cost to 6 and increase the area to a 15 ft square.<br><br>The fifth step allows you to increase the Cost to 8 and increase the area to a 20 ft square.</p>\n",
